85,737,474       + 12.2      734,664,964     + 19.3
Foods/Food Products             
79,451,377       + 24.0      616,345,427     + 33.5
Apparel/Footwear/Accessories    
46,842,297       -  4.0      541,338,674     +  7.9
Drugs/Remedies                  
50,426,047       + 32.3      461,490,113     + 12.2
