service this spring.  ITT is scheduled to deliver 100,000 of the
chip sets in the next few months.  BSB has long contended its use
of D-MAC technology--and its compatibility with existing TV sets
and future widescreen and advanced formats--instead of PAL
technology has provided it with a "technological hammerlock" over
rival Sky Television.



