WORKSHOP TO GUIDE NIST'S TRANSITION TO NATIONAL ADVANCED MANUFACTURING
TESTBED

    July 12:  The Next Research Step in the Manufacturing Revolution:
A Workshop to Guide NIST's Transition to the National Advanced Manu-
facturing Testbed, at NIST Gaithersburg.  The purpose is to officially
close the Automated Manufacturing Research Facility and to introduce
the new National Advanced Manufacturing Testbed.  (Dave Stieren, B113
Metrology Bldg., NIST, Gaithersburg, MD 20899, 301/975-3197, email:
dstieren+enh.nist.gov.)



