50TH CALORIMETRY CONFERENCE

     July 23-28:  50th Calorimetry Conference, at NIST Gaithersburg. 
The purpose is to report on and discuss topics associated with
calorimetry and chemical thermodynamics.  NIST and the Department of
Energy are sponsors. (Robert Goldberg, A353 Chemistry Bldg., NIST,
Gaithersburg, MD 20899, 301/975-2584, email: goldber+tiber.nist.gov.)



