TEKTRONIX TEST SYSTEM SOLD

Beaverton, Ore.-based Tektronix has delivered a $1.6 million
semiconductor automated logic test system, called "Vista" to
Hughes Aircraft Corp.'s electro-optical data systems group in El
Segundo, Calif. "We went through an extensive hands-on
